CLASS QSound INHERIT QObject

   DATA self_destruction INIT .F.

   METHOD new
   METHOD delete
   METHOD fileName
   METHOD isFinished
   METHOD loops
   METHOD loopsRemaining
   METHOD setLoops
   METHOD play1
   METHOD stop
   METHOD isAvailable
   METHOD play2
   METHOD play
   DESTRUCTOR destroyObject

